{
  "stem": "9446.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's unfortunate that I didn't speak any English then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My-- all my English, whatever I know, is acquired in the United States during the 46 years I am here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came without any knowledge of English at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'd like to think that I inherited a little bit of my father's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ability to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] do things which require some mechanical skills a little bit.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was an electrical engineer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was very good in-- in anything that has to do with mechanics and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had just a little bit of it, not much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What I will say that-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] yeah, I shouldn't forget to mention to you, I had to go to several schools.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Originally, we started with a Polish school, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I say Polish, I mean it was a private school owned by some Polish institution, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But eventually, anti-Semitisim got so unbearable that my father took me out from that school, and I had to go-- I went to Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now when I say Jewish school, I don't mean that it was teaching just Jewish subjects, or had anything to do with Jewish religion at all.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No, unfortunately I wish it had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was Jewish school, because it was owned by a group of Jewish teachers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a private, as I said, gymnasium as I called it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not that I called it that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's the way it was called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, when the war broke out in 1939 between Poland and Germany on September 1st, so it completely destroyed all my dreams and my plans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was planning on studying in university.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was two years studying psychology in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
